               <h3>Building Sustainable Collections of Free Third-Party Web Resources</h3>
               </i></b>
         by <b>Louis A. Pitschmann</b>
         
         
         <blockquote>
            June 2001 <br>
            <i>Copyright 2001 by the Council on Library and Information Resources. No part of this publication may be reproduced or transcribed
